WEBVTT

00:02:00.200 --> 00:02:03.696
So a group of journalists, including me,

00:02:03.720 --> 00:02:07.656
started a website
to investigate this fake news.

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:09.960
We called it StopFake.

00:02:10.600 --> 00:02:12.216
The idea was simple:

00:02:12.240 --> 00:02:16.576
take a piece of news,
check it with verifiable proof

00:02:16.600 --> 00:02:20.096
like photos, videos
and other strong evidence.

00:02:20.120 --> 00:02:23.640
If it turns out to be fake,
we put it on our website.

00:02:24.600 --> 00:02:28.216
Now, StopFake is an informational hub

00:02:28.240 --> 00:02:31.680
which analyzes propaganda
in all its phases.